# apinsee

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of apinsee is to ease access to Insee APIs available at <https://api.insee.fr/>

## Installation

You can install the development version from [GitHub](https://github.com/) with:

``` r
remotes::install_github("rlesur/apinsee")
```
